rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Relationship collecting the data for the CO2 emissions statistics for a given region. This type includes the region, the date and amount, and the type of emissions measured.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: CO2 Emission Type

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.co2_emissions_type to the amount of emissions measured for the date given.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Emissions Amount

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:co2_emissions_type to the mso:statistics.environment_group that the emissions are for.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Region

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.co2_emissions_type to the sector responsible for those emissions.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Sector

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Population of Type
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Relationship type relating a region to a type found in the region. Properties on this relationship type include date of validity for the population number and the number of the type in the region. This is a very broad relationship type, including the number of moose in Canada, the population of Windows phones in Redmond, and the number of teacups in Great Britian. For an extensive set of properties on the human population in a region, see statistics.population_group.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Count of Type
rdf:Description.mso:type.type.deprecation_info: This type is too broadly defined and allows the creation of key/value pairs with opaque semantics. DeprecatedBy:[REDMOND\ianiles]

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating a population of type relationship to the date the fact is valid for. For example, if the number of polydactyl cats in Ket West in 2013 is 50, then the date of the fact validity is "2013". The date the fact is valid could mean the data was gathered during that time, or the data was published during that date.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Date
rdf:Description.mso:type.property.deprecation_info: The type of this property has been deprecated. DeprecatedBy:[REDMOND\ianiles]

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property type relating a population of type relationship to the number of entities of the type found within the location. For example, if the number of polydactyl cats in Ket West in 2013 is 50, then the number of the population in the fact is "50".
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Population Number
rdf:Description.mso:type.property.deprecation_info: The type of this property has been deprecated. DeprecatedBy:[REDMOND\ianiles]

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating a population of type relationship to the region the population is found in. For example, if the number of polydactyl cats in Ket West in 2013 is 50, then the region in this fact is "Key West".
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Population Region
rdf:Description.mso:type.property.deprecation_info: The type of this property has been deprecated. DeprecatedBy:[REDMOND\ianiles]

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating a population of type relationship to the type of thing the population is. For example, if the number of polydactyl cats in Ket West in 2013 is 50, then the population type in the fact is "polydactyl cat". This property is intentionally broad, so that we can also represent the population of chocolate teapots in Colorado in 1993, or the population of Windows phones in Redmond.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Population Type
rdf:Description.mso:type.property.deprecation_info: The type of this property has been deprecated. DeprecatedBy:[REDMOND\ianiles]

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A relationship type that collects information about the incidences of categories of crime, e.g. violent crime, robbery, burglary, etc.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Crime Rate by Type

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that specifies the type of crime for which incidence information is provided.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Category

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that specifies the number of people per hundred thousand in the given population who were victims of the given type of crime in the specified time frame.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Type collecting the statistics for the economic activity for a group or within a location.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Economic Statistics

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the adjusted net national income. This figure takes the net national income (NNI) and adjusts it for natural resource depletion.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Adjusted Net National Income

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the percentage that is the net output of the Agriculture sector as percentage of GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Agriculture (% of GDP)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the net output of the agriculture sector as a percentage of the GDP. Value added is the net output of a sector after adding up all outputs and subtracting intermediate inputs and is calculated without making deductions for depreciation of fabricated assets or depletion and degradation of natural resources.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Agriculture, Value Added (% of GDP)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the value added in agriculture measures the output of the agricultural sector (ISIC divisions 1-5) less the value of intermediate inputs. Agriculture comprises value added from forestry, hunting, and fishing as well as cultivation of crops and livestock production.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Agriculture Value Added per Worker (Constant 2005 US$)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its ratio of bank capital and reserves to total assets.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Bank Capital to Assets Ratio

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the percentage of emigrants with at least one year of tertiary education ages 25 and older.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Emigration of University Educated Workforce

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Start-up Procedures to Register a Business (Number)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the number of days needed to start-up a new business.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Business Start-up Procedures

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its cash surplus or deficit as a percentage of its GDP. This is the revenue (including grants) minus expense, minus net acquisition of nonfinancial assets.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Cash Surplus or Deficit

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the percentage of children 7-14 engaged in any economic activity for at least an hour during the reference week. This includes those children working and not attending school.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Child Labor (% of children ages 7-14)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group its consumer price index. This statistic represents the changes in cost to the average consumer.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Consumer Price Index

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the dated percentage that is the rate of inflation as measured by the consumer price index. Inflation as measured by the consumer price index reflects the annual percentage change in the cost to the average consumer of acquiring a basket of goods and services that may be fixed or changed at specified intervals, such as yearly.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Inflation Measured by the Consumer Price Index

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its current account balance, which is the sum of net exports of goods and services, net primary income, and net secondary income.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Current Account Balance

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the percentage that is the rate paid by commercial or other banks for demand, time, or savings deposits.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Deposit Interest Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Depth of credit information index (0=low to 8=high)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its place in the credit information index, which measures rules affecting the scope, accessibility, and quality of credit information available through public or private credit registries.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Depth of Credit Information Index

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group.diesel_fuel_price to the dated price per liter paid at the pump.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Diesel Price Per Liter

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its pump price of diesel fuel.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Diesel Price (per Liter)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Documents to Export (Number)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the number of documents required per shipment to export goods.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Documents to Export

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Documents to Import (Number)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the number of documents required per shipment to import goods.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Documents to Import

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Domestic Credit Provided by Financial Sector (% of GDP)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to all credit to various sectors on a gross basis from the financial sector as a percentage of its GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Domestic Credit Provided by Financial Sector

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Domestic Credit to Private Sector (% of GDP)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the financial resources provided to the private sector by financial corporations as a percentage of its GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Domestic Credit to Private Sector

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Ease of Doing Business Index (1=Most Business-friendly Regulations)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its rank in the ease of doing business index. This index ranks economies from 1 to 189, with first place being the best. A high rank means that the regulatory environment is conducive to business operation.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Ease of Doing Business Index

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates an economic group to information about employers in the economic group.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Employer by Type

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the investment in energy projects with private participation. This covers infrastructure projects in energy that have reached financial closure and directly or indirectly serve the public.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Investment in Energy with Private Participation (Current US$)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its expenses as a percentage of its GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Expense (% of GDP)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its export value index, which is the current value of exports (f.o.b.) converted to U.S. dollars and expressed as a percentage of the average for the base period.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Export Value Index

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Export Volume Index (2000 = 100)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its export volume index, which is the ratio of the export value index to the corresponding unit value index.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Export Volume Index

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its export of goods and services as a percentage of its GDP. Goods and services include merchandise, freight, insurance, transport, travel, royalties, license fees, and other services, such as communication, construction, financial, information, business, personal, and government services.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Exports of Goods and Services

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to another mso:statistics.economic_group, which is an export partner to the first.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Exports Partners

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the rank of the entity's exports as compared to others.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Exports Rank

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the value of its exports.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Exports Value

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the external debt owed by this entity.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: External Debt

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the rank of this entity's external debt.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: External Debt Rank

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the amount of external debt stock, which is the total external debt owed to nonresidents repayable in foreign currency, goods, or services.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: External Debt Stock

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its private, nonguaranteed external debt, which is the long-term external obligations of private debtors that are not guaranteed for repayment by a public entity.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Private Non-guaranteed External Debt Stocks

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: External Debt Stocks, Public and Publicly Guaranteed (PPG) (DOD, Current US$)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its public and publicly guaranteed debt, which is the long-term external obligations of public debtors, including the national government, political subdivisions (or an agency of either), and autonomous public bodies, and external obligations of private debtors that are guaranteed for repayment by a public entity.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Public and Publicly Guaranteed External Debt Stocks

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: External Debt Stocks, Short-term (DOD, Current US$)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its debt that has an original maturity of one year or less.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Short-term External Debt Stocks

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the percentage of the employed women in the labor force.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Female Labor Force Participation Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the percentage of firms using banks to finance investments.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Firms Using Banks to Finance Investment (% of Firms)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the amount of direct foreign investment to acquire management in its enterprises.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Foreign Direct Investment, Net Inflows

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the entity's reserves of foreign exchange and gold.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Foreign Exchange Reserves

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its rank of foreign exchange reserves.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Foreign Exchange Reserves Rank

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the dated price of gasoline paid at the pump.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Gasoline Price Per Liter

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Nominal GDP
Nominal Gross Domestic Product
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its nominal GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Gross Domestic Product

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the rate of price change in the economy as a whole.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: GDP deflator change

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its growth rate for the GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: GDP Growth Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the percentage of change of the real GDP as compared to the previous year.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: GDP Growth Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Per Capita GDP
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its per capita GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Per Capita Gross Domestic Product

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the GDP per person employed. This is the GDP divided by total employment in the economy. Purchasing power parity (PPP) GDP is GDP converted to 1990 constant international dollars using PPP rates.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: GDP Per Employed Person

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the GDP per unit of energy use. This is the PPP GDP per kilogram of oil equivalent of energy use. PPP GDP is gross domestic product converted to 2005 constant international dollars using purchasing power parity rates.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: GDP Per Unit Of Energy Use

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: GDP Rank
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group its nominal GDP rank.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Gross Domestic Product Rank

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: roperty relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the measure the U.S. dollar price change in the stock markets covered by the S&P/IFCI and S&P/Frontier BMI country indices.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: S&P Global Equity Indices (Annual % Change)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its GNI in the Atlas Method.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: GNI, Atlas Method

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the entity's GNI in constant 2005 U.S. dollars. GNI is the sum of value added by all resident producers plus any product taxes (less subsidies) not included in the valuation of output plus net receipts of primary income (compensation of employees and property income) from abroad.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: GNI in Constant 2005 U.S. dollars

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the percentage of GNI growth.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: GNI Growth

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the gross national income in purchasing power parity in a currency to adjust for price level differences across locations. See also mso:statistics.economic_group.gni_in_ppp_per_capita.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: GNI in PPP

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the gross national income per capita in purchasing power parity in a currency. See also mso:statistics.economic_group.gni_in_ppp.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: GDP in PPP per Capita

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: GNI per Capita, Atlas Method (Current US$)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its GNI per capita as caluculated by the Atlas Method. The GNI in local currency is converted into U.S. dollars using the Atlas conversion factor, which uses a three-year average of exchange rates, adjusted for the difference between the rate of inflation and that in a number of developed countries.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: GNI per Capita, Atlas Method

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Gross Capital Formation (% of GDP)
Gross Domestic Investment
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its gross capital formation, which is outlays on additions to the fixed assets of the economy plus net changes in the level of inventories.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Gross Capital Formation

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the gross savings as a percentage of GDP. Gross savings are calculated as gross national income less total consumption, plus net transfers.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Gross Savings (% of GDP)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Health Expenditure per Capita (Current US$)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its health expenditures per capita.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Health Expenditure per Capita

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.government_group to the health expenditures of the government as a percentage of the government's GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Health Expenditure (% of GDP)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Health Expenditure, Public (% of Total Health Expenditure)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its public health expenditures as a percentage of its total health expenditures. Public health expenditures are recurrent and capital spending from government budgets, external borrowings and grants, and social health insurance funds.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Public Health Expenditure

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the percentage of high tech manufactured exports in a given economic group.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: High-tech as % of manufactured exports

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: High-technology Exports (Current US$)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its high-technology exports, which are the products with high R&D intensity, such as in aerospace, computers, pharmaceuticals, scientific instruments, and electrical machinery.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: High-technology Exports

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its percentage of exports that are high technology products.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: High Technology Exports Percentage

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the market value of all goods and services, including durable products, purchased by households. It excludes purchases of dwellings but includes imputed rent for owner-occupied dwellings.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Household consumption expenditures (% of GDP)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: International Bank for Reconstruction and Development Loans and International Development Association Credits IBRD Loans and IDA Credits (DOD, current US$)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its International Bank for Reconstruction and Development (IBRD) loans and International Development Association (IDA) credits, which are public and publicly guaranteed debt extended by the World Bank Group.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: IBRD Loans and IDA Credits

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: ICT Goods Exports (% of Total Goods Exports)
Information and Communication Technology Goods Exports
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its information and communication technology goods exports as a percentage of total exports. These exports include telecommunications, audio and video, computer and related equipment; electronic components; and other information and communication technology goods.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: ICT Goods Exports

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: ICT Goods Imports (% Total Goods Imports)
Information and Communication Technology Goods Imports
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its information and communication technology goods exports as a percentage of total imports. These imports include telecommunications, audio and video, computer and related equipment; electronic components; and other information and communication technology goods.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: ICT Goods Imports

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: ICT Service Exports (% of Service Exports, BoP)
Information and Communication Technology Service Exports
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its information and communication technology service exports as a percentage of service exports. Services include computer and communications services and information services.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: ICT Service Exports

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: IDA Resource Allocation Index (1=low to 6=high)
IRAI
International Development Association Resource Allocation Index
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its IDA Resource Allocation Index, which is obtained by calculating the average score for each of 16 clusters and then by averaging those scores.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: IDA Resource Allocation Index

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the value of all goods and other market services received from the rest of the world as a percentage of GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Imports of Goods and Services

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Import Value Index (2000 = 100)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its import value index. This index is computed by taking the current value of its imports converted to U.S. dollars and expressed as a percentage of the average for the base period.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Import Value Index

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Import Volume Index (2000 = 100)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its import volume index, which is the ratio of the import value indexes to the corresponding unit value indexes.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Import Volume Index

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to another mso:statistics.economic_group that is an import partner to the first.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Imports Partners

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its imports rank.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Imports Rank

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the value of its imports.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Imports Value

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the percentage of GDP that is the net output of the Industry sector, which includes mining, manufacturing, and utilities, as a percentage of the GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Industry (% of GDP)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the net output of the industry sector after adding up all outputs and subtracting intermediate inputs.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Industry, Value Added (% of GDP)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the inflation as measured by the annual growth rate of the GDP implicit deflator and shows the rate of price change in the economy as a whole.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: GDP Deflator Inflation

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economics_group to its inflation rate.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Inflation Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economics_group to its inflation rate rank.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Inflation Rate Rank

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Interest Rate Spread (Lending Rate Minus Deposit Rate, %)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its interest rate spread, which is the interest rate charged by banks on loans to private sector customers minus the interest rate paid by commercial or similar banks for demand, time, or savings deposits.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Interest Rate Spread

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the percentage of its firms having an internationally-recognized quality certification, i.e., International Organization for Standardization (ISO) 9000, 9002 or 14000.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Internationally-recognized Quality Certification (% of Firms)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economics_group to the number of people in its labor force.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Labor Force Size

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economics_group to the mso:statistics.labor_force_occupation entity collecting data on labor force data by occupation.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Labor Force Occupation Percentages

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the percentage of its total labor force actually employed.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Labor Force Participation Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its labor force rank.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Labor Force World Rank

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the interest rate charged by banks on loans to prime customers.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Lending Interest Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the mso:location.import_export relationship with data on its imports and exports.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Major Exports

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economics_group to its major imported commodities, instances of mso:location.import_export.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Major Imports

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the percentage of its male labor force actually employed.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Male Labor Force Participation Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the market value of all stock listed companies, which is the share price times the number of outstanding shares. This is expressed as a percentage of the group's GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Market Capitalization of Listed Companies (% of GDP)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Market Capitalization of Listed Companies (Current US$)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the share price of its listed companies times the number of shares outstanding.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Market Capitalization of Listed Companies

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the median time (the value for 50 percent of shipments) from shipment point to port of loading.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Median Lead Time to Export

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the median time (the value for 50 percent of shipments) from port of discharge to arrival at the consignee.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Median Lead Time to Import

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its merchandise trade as a share of GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Merchandise Trade Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its minimum wage, which does not include tips, allowances, or value of other benefits.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Minimum Wage

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its growth rate in money and quasi money. This is the sum of currency outside banks, demand deposits other than those of the central government, and the time, savings, and foreign currency deposits of resident sectors other than the central government.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Money and Quasi Money Growth

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Net Barter Terms of Trade Index (2000 = 100)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its net barter terms of trade index. This is calculated the percentage ratio of the export unit value indexes to the import unit value indexes, measured relative to the base year.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Net Barter Terms of Trade Index

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its net flows on long-term external debt. Long-term external debt is the debt that has an original or extended maturity of more than one year and that is owed to nonresidents by residents of an economy and repayable in currency, goods, or services.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Net Flows on Long-term External Debt

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its net flows on its total external debt. Net flows on external debt are disbursements on long-term external debt and IMF purchases minus principal repayments on long-term external debt.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Net Flows on Total External Debt

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Portfolio Equity, Net Inflows (BoP, Current US$)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its net inflows from equity securities other than those recorded as direct investment and including shares, stocks, depository receipts (American or global), and direct purchases of shares in local stock markets by foreign investors.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Net Inflows from Portfolio Equity

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its net official development assistance and other other official aid from official donors.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Net Official Development Assistance and Official Aid Received (Current US$)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its official development assistance received per capita. ODA is development aid provided by the member states of the Development Assistance Committee.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Net ODA Received per Capita

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Net ODA Received (% of GNI)
Net Official Development Assistance as Percentage of GNI
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its official development assistance received as a percentage of GNI. ODA is development aid provided by the member states of the Development Assistance Committee.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Net ODA Received

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: New Businesses Registered (Number)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the number of new limited liability corporations registered in the calendar year.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: New Businesses Registered

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the value of nonperforming loans divided by the total value of the loan portfolio (including nonperforming loans before the deduction of specific loan-loss provisions).
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Bank Nonperforming Loans to Total Gross Loans (%)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its published official development assistance received, which is an indicator of international aid flow.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Official Development Assistance Received

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the official exchange rate of its currency.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Official Exchange Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Personal Remittances, Received (Current US$)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to all current transfers in cash or in kind made or received by resident households to or from nonresident households.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Personal Remittances Received

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the mean shortfall from the poverty line at $1.25 per day, expressed as a percentage of the poverty line.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Poverty Gap at $1.25 a Day (PPP) (%)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the mean shortfall from the poverty line at $2 per day, expressed as a percentage of the poverty line.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Poverty Headcount Ratio at $2 a Day (PPP) (% of Population)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its poverty gap at the mso:statistics.economic_group poverty lines.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Poverty Gap at National Poverty Lines (%)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the poverty headcount ratio at the poverty lines of the mso:statistics.economic_group.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Poverty Headcount Ratio at National Poverty Lines (% of Population)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the percentage of the population living on less than $2 a day, at the 2005 international prices.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Poverty Rate ($2 per day)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Private Credit Bureau Coverage (% of Adults)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the number of individuals or firms listed by a private credit bureau with current information on repayment history, unpaid debts, or credit outstanding.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Private Credit Bureau Coverage

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Public Credit Registry Coverage (% of adults)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the number of individuals and firms listed in a public credit registry with current information on repayment history, unpaid debts, or credit outstanding as a percentage of the adult population.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Public Credit Registry Coverage

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Public Spending on Education, Total (% of GDP)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its total public expenditure on education expressed as a percentage of the Gross Domestic Product (GDP) in a given year.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Total Public Spending on Education as Percentage of GDP

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Public Spending on Education, Total (% of Government Expenditure)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its total public education expenditure expressed as a percentage of total government expenditure for all sectors in a given financial year.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Total Public Spending on Education as Percentage of Government Expenditure

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the real gross domestic product. This is a macroeconomic measure that takes the nominal GDP adjusted for price changes, like inflation or deflation. This transform the measure into an index for quantity of total output.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Real GDP

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Real Interest Rate (%)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its real interest rate, which is the lending interest rate adjusted for inflation as measured by the GDP deflator.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Real Interest Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its percentage of GDP spent on research and development.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Research and Development Expenditure Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economics_group to its average number of researchers engaged in research and development (per million people).
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Research and Development Researchers per Million

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its average number of technicians engaged in research and development (per million people).
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Research and Development Technicians per Million

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates an economic group to information about the revenue generated by particular industrial sectors in the economic group.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Revenue by Sector

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Risk Premium on Lending (Lending Rate Minus Treasury Bill Rate, %)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the interest rate charged by banks on loans to private sector customers minus the "risk free" treasury bill interest rate at which short-term government securities are issued or traded in the market.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Risk Premium on Lending

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its rural poverty gap.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Rural Poverty Gap at National Poverty Lines (%)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its rural poverty headcount ratio.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Rural Poverty Headcount Ratio at National Poverty Lines (% of Rural Population)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Secondary Income, Other Sectors, Payments (BoP, Current US$)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group.secondary_income to its secondary income, which refers to transfers recorded in the balance of payments whenever an economy provides or receives goods, services, income, or financial items without a quid pro quo.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Secondary Income

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the percentage of the GDP that is the net output of of the service industry.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Services (% of GDP)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its services trade as a share of GDP (percentage).
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Services Trade Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its services value added as a percentage of its GDP. Value added in the service sector include value added in wholesale and retail trade, transport, and government, financial, professional, and personal services such as education, health care, and real estate services.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Services, Etc., Value Added (% of GDP)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Number of Visits or Required Meetings with Tax Officials
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group number of visits or required meetings with tax officials during the year.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Meetings with Tax Officials

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to investment in telecom projects with private participation. This covers infrastructure projects in telecommunications that have reached financial closure and directly or indirectly serve the public.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Investment in Telecoms with Private Participation (Current US$)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the amount of time required to start a new business.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Time to Start a Business

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the number of the domestically incorporated companies listed on its stock exchanges.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Total Listed Domesticated Companies

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its holdings of monetary gold, special drawing rights, reserves of IMF members held by the IMF, and holdings of foreign exchange under the control of monetary authorities.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Total Reserves

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the amount of taxes and mandatory contributions payable by businesses after accounting for allowable deductions and exemptions as a percentage of commercial profits.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Total Tax Rate (% of Commercial Profits)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its trade balance as a percentage of the GDP. This is the external balance on goods and services (formerly resource balance) equals exports of goods and services minus imports of goods and services (previously non-factor services).
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Trade Balance (% of GDP)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its trade in services, which is the sum of service exports and imports divided by the value of GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Trade in Services (% of GDP)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to investment in transport projects with private participation. This covers infrastructure projects in transport that have reached financial closure and directly or indirectly serve the public.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Investment in Transport with Private Participation (Current US$)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the total value of shares traded divided by the average market capitalization.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Turnover Ratio of Stocks Traded

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the urban poverty headcount ratio at the poverty lines of the mso:statistics.economic_group.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Urban Poverty Headcount Ratio at National Poverty Lines (% of Urban Population)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to its total value of shares traded.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Total Value Stocks Traded

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to investment in water and sanitation projects with private participation. This covers infrastructure projects in water and sanitation that have reached financial closure and directly or indirectly serve the public.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Investment in Water and Sanitation with Private Participation (Current US$)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.economic_group to the price of a representative basket of wholesale goods. Some countries use this as a measure of inflation.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Wholesale Price Index

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Type collecting the statistics for a group or location's educational efforts.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Education Statistics

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates an education group to the average starting salary earned by members/graduates of the group.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Average Salary

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the number of people that have graduated from college.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: High School Graduate Population

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the number of people that are computer specialists.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Computer Specialist Population

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to its rank on percentage of GDP spent on education.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Education Expenditure Rank

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to its percentage of GDP spent on education.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Education Expenditure Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the number of people that are engineers.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Engineer Population

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to its spending per primary student as a percentage of the per capita GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Expenditure per Primary Student

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Expenditure per Student, Secondary (% of GDP per Capita)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to its spending per secondary student as a percentage of the per capita GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Expenditure per Secondary Student

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Expenditure per Student, Tertiary (% of GDP per Capita)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to its spending per tertiary student as a percentage of the per capita GDP.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Expenditure per Tertiary Student

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the total number of female primary-school-age children who are not enrolled in either primary or secondary schools.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Female Children out of Primary School

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Gross Intake Ratio in First Grade of Primary Education, Female (% of Relevant Age Group)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the number of new female entrants in the first grade of primary education regardless of age, expressed as a percentage of the population of the official primary entrance age.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Female Gross Intake Ratio in First Grade of Primary Education

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Persistence to Last Grade of Primary, Female (% of Cohort)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to its share of female children enrolled in the first grade of primary school who eventually reach the last grade of primary.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Female Persistence to Last Grade of Primary

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Primary Completion Rate, Female (% of Relevant Age Group)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the measure of the gross intake ratio to the last grade of primary education for female students.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Female Primary Completion Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Repeaters, Primary, Female (% of Female Enrollment)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the number of female students repeating a primary level as a percentage of all female enrollment.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Female Primary Repeaters

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Progression to Secondary School, Female (%)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the number of new female entrants to the first grade of secondary education as a percentage of the female population.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Female Progression to Secondary School

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Literacy Rate, Youth Female (% of Females Ages 15-24)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the literacy rate among females 15 to 24.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Female Youth Literacy Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates an instance of an education group to the average amount of merit-based financial aid received by first year students.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: First Year Students Average Merit-based Financial Aid

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates an instance of an education group to the average amount of need-based financial aid received by first year students.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: First Year Students Average Need-based Financial Aid

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates an instance of an education group to the average amount of self-help financial aid received by first year students.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: First Year Students Average Self-help Financial Aid

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates an instance of an education group to the percentage of first-year students who receive some form of merit-based financial aid.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: First Year Students Receiving Merit-based Financial Aid

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates an instance of an education group to the percentage of first-year students who receive some form of need-based financial aid.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: First Year Students Receiving Need-based Financial Aid

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates an instance of an education group to the percentage of first-year students who receive some form of financial aid that requires the students to perform work in exchange for the funds.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: First Year Students Receiving Self-help Financial Aid

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: School Enrollment, Preprimary (% Gross)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to its preprimary school enrollment as a percentage of total gross enrollment.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Gross Preprimary School Enrollment

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: School Enrollment, Primary (% Gross)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to its primary school enrollment as a percentage of total gross enrollment.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Gross Primary School Enrollment

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: School Enrollment, Secondary (% Gross)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to its secondary school enrollment as a percentage of total gross enrollment.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Gross Secondary School Enrollment

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: School Enrollment, Tertiary (% Gross)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to its tertiary school enrollment as a percentage of total gross enrollment.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Gross Tertiary School Enrollment

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the number of people that have graduated from high school.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: High School Graduate Population

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates an education group to the highest starting salary earned by a member/graduate of the group.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Highest Salary

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the number of people that are life or physical scientists.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Life and Physical Scientist Population

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the percentage of people that can read.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Literacy Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates an education group to the lowest starting salary earned by a member/graduate of the group.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Lowest Salary

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the total number of male primary-school-age children who are not enrolled in either primary or secondary schools.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Male Children out of Primary School

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Gross Intake Ratio in First Grade of Primary Education, Male (% of Relevant Age Group)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the number of new male entrants in the first grade of primary education regardless of age, expressed as a percentage of the population of the official primary entrance age.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Male Gross Intake Ratio in First Grade of Primary Education

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to its share of male children enrolled in the first grade of primary school who eventually reach the last grade of primary.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Persistence to Last Grade of Primary, Male (% of Cohort)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Primary Completion Rate, Male (% of Relevant Age Group)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the measure of the gross intake ratio to the last grade of primary education for male students.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Male Primary Completion Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Repeaters, Primary, Male (% of Male Enrollment)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.education_group to the number of male students repeating a primary level as a percentage of all male enrollment.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Male Primary Repeaters

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Progression to Secondary School, Male (%)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Pupil-teacher Ratio, Primary

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Environmental Statistics

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Agricultural Methane Emissions (% of Total)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Arable Land (Hectares per Person)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.environment_group to the percentage of arable land in the region. Arable land refers to the land cultivated for crops. rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Percentage of Arable Land

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.environment_group to its average precipitation in inches.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Average Annual Precipitation

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.environment_group to the amount of metric tons of cereal, specifically dry grains like wheat, rice, barley, and oats, the group produced.

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Crop Production Index

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.alias: Fertilizer Consumption (Kilograms per Hectare of Arable Land)
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.environment_group to its fertilizer consumption in kilograms per hectare of its arable land.

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:statistics.environment_group to its food production index, which covers food crops that are considered edible and that contain nutrients.

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: GEF Benefits Index for Biodiversity
